<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>雪茄 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E9%9B%AA%E8%8C%84/</link><description>Recent content in 雪茄 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Tue, 11 Oct 2011 13:57:12 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E9%9B%AA%E8%8C%84/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>法律健全的经典案例</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/classic-case-of-a-sound-legal/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Oct 2011 13:57:12 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/classic-case-of-a-sound-legal/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了一个法律案例。一名名叫Charlotte的律师买了一盒昂贵的雪茄并为其投保火险。律师在一个月内将雪茄抽完后要求保险公司赔偿。保险公司拒绝赔偿，但律师通过法院判决迫使保险公司支付了15000美元的赔偿。然而，保险公司报警将律师逮捕，指控他有24起纵火案。律师因此被判刑24个月，并罚款24000美元。这个故事被选为最佳犯罪律师竞赛奖的第一名。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/classic-case-of-a-sound-legal/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>